310
00:53:54.773 --> 00:53:57.651
<span style="style.default_1">Honey. where are you?
Why didn't you tell me?</span>

311
00:53:57.734 --> 00:54:00.696
<span style="style.default_1">You promised to be with me.
I'm still upset</span>

312
00:54:00.779 --> 00:54:02.614
-your father puked on me.
-Honey. I...

313
00:54:02.698 --> 00:54:05.325
