355
00:59:29.149 --> 00:59:29.983
Ruben.

356
00:59:36.907 --> 00:59:39.117
"Dark priestesses.

357
00:59:39.201 --> 00:59:44.748
Usually. these women
have dedicated themselves

358
00:59:44.831 --> 00:59:48.251
