435
01:15:18.970 --> 01:15:21.183
-Your brother and sister chose me. Maya.
-Your brother and sister chose me. Maya.

436
01:15:24.437 --> 01:15:25.730
-Maya.
-Maya.

437
01:15:27.398 --> 01:15:29.483
-You're scared. aren't you?
-You're scared. aren't you?

438
01:15:33.738 --> 01:15:35.281
